  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The patients are assigned by randomisation on one of the two laxatives. After cleansing they
      have to fill in an evaluation form to report their findings and difficulties. Also the
      surgeon will be asked to fill in a score-form to report all details concerning the bowel
      preparation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
